Variable: Data are presented as n (%) or median (IQR).
IMDC = International Metastatic Renal Cell Carcinoma Database Consortium

IO-TKI: pembrolizumab plus axitinib/nivolumab plus cabozantinib/pembrolizumab plus lenvatinib.
